# Vercel AI Gateway Configuration
# The AI Gateway is automatically configured through Vercel's integration system.
# No additional configuration needed for OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, or other supported providers.

# FAL AI Configuration (for image and video generation)
# Get your FAL key from https://fal.ai/dashboard
FAL_KEY=your_fal_api_key_here

# Optional: You can also add specific provider keys if needed
# These are handled through Vercel AI Gateway by default
# OPENAI_API_KEY=your_key_here (not needed with AI Gateway)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_key_here (not needed with AI Gateway)
